      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2511_01_04/sud_vo_adv_event_2511_01_04-rio005.wav",
      "text": "私と葵は忘れかけていた情熱を取り戻した……",
